OL,6,FA teacher who groomed and sexually
OL,7,Fabused a teenage pupil has been
OL,8,Fdescribed as a "cold, calculating
OL,9,Fchild predator".
OL,11,FJudith Evans was jailed for two years
OL,12,Fat Belfast Crown Court on Friday for a
OL,13,Fseries of sexual offences against a
OL,14,Fschoolboy and placed on the sex
OL,15,Foffender register for life.
OL,17,FThe court heard that when Judith Evans
OL,18,Fwas confronted with her crimes by
OL,19,Fpolice, she had falsely claimed that
OL,20,Fher teenage victim had threatened and
OL,21,Fraped her.
