OL,6,FJudge Patricia Smyth said there had
OL,7,Fbeen close to 10,000 text messages
OL,8,Fexchanged between the teacher and
OL,9,Fpupil.
OL,11,FThe judge said the teacher had basked
OL,12,Fin her victim's "adolescent attraction
OL,13,Ftowards her".
OL,15,FEvans, 33, from Elmwood Grove in
OL,16,FNewtownabbey, was a teacher at Belfast
OL,17,FBoys' Model School when the offences
OL,18,Foccurred.
