OL,6,FFollowing sentencing, PSNI detective
OL,7,Fchief inspector Jill Duffie said:
OL,8,F"Evans is a cold, calculating child
OL,9,Fpredator who was in a position of
OL,10,Ftrust and abused that position by
OL,11,Ftaking advantage of a young boy who
OL,12,Fwas her pupil at the time.
OL,14,F"She preyed on his vulnerabilities and
OL,15,Fbuilt an inappropriate friendship with
OL,16,Fthe boy before then further grooming
OL,17,Fhim and sexually exploiting him.
OL,19,F"The messages exchanged between her
OL,20,Fand her underage pupil were highly
OL,21,Fsexual and nothing short of sickening."
