OL,13,Fsexual communication with a child,
OL,14,Fmeeting a child following sexual
OL,15,Fgrooming, sexual activity with a child
OL,16,Finvolving penetration and possessing
OL,17,Findecent images of the schoolboy.
OL,18,FThese offences were committed between
